    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been my absolute baby\u2014it\u2019s in truly incredible condition, looking and smelling just like it did the day I drove it home. I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it with regular detailing, so it\u2019s basically spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
