      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul and documented subframe reinforcement for structural rigidity. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate entry, paired with a fresh clutch and a perfectly dialed M Variable Differential Lock. Every suspension component remains within factory tolerances, utilizing OEM dampers to maintain the original handling geometry. With zero thermal cycling fatigue on the cooling system and a pristine undercarriage, this is a turn-key masterpiece for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
