    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its original deep-gloss factory finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and carries that distinct new-car aroma, completely free from any wear, creasing, or imperfections. Every switch, dial, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; the vehicle comes with a comprehensive, chronological folder of service records from a certified master technician, ensuring the engine runs with whisper-quiet precision and the transmission shifts seamlessly. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. The sale includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker.",
